Firestrikes blade scraped against Menasor's thick armor. Menasor felt
that, and for a second forgot where he was. Instinctivly he held
Slaughter strongly with one hand, but he now had another attacker, he
made a large backhanding motion with the hand that was being sliced by
Firestrike, to send the Decepticon realing.

Megatron had lost interest for a minute, he nodded to Shockwave, and
mentioned that they would be in touch, as he left.
